channel.title: Nashville, TN: Anybody here?
channel.description:
I moved to Nashville from Los Angeles last Summer and I haven't found many actual bootstrappers here.
If you're currently bootstrapping, and you are in Nashville, and you are interested in meeting in person from time to time please let me know!
Thanks, Oliver
